        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2286055319" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17682375769740208572">Scarlet thread ⭐️<br/><br/>I dont know how she makes me fall in love with the characters so quickly. Everything she writes is pure gold. <br/><br/>She is a rich white girl, he is an average hispanic boy. Their parents dont approve but love is love an unstoppable love. <br/><br/>They get married and start a family and everything is perfect. That is until that unstoppable love sees reality in the harsh world. </span>

          </span>
